headline: Stryker Launches Incompass Total Ankle System at AOFAS 2025
summary: PORTAGE, Mich., September 09, 2025--Stryker will launch its Incompass™ Total Ankle System at the 2025 AOFAS Annual Meeting in Savannah, Georgia, September 10–13, 2025 (booth # 401).
